程序包 model.mapping

类 VideoTypeMapping

java.lang.Object
model.mapping.VideoTypeMapping
public class VideoTypeMapping
extends java.lang.Object
Map VideoType to JSON database. This "JSON database" is a self-defined database and it should only be used in this software. Offering add, find, search methods for video type data
从以下版本开始:
23 April 2021
版本:
1.0
作者:
Zai Song
